title: [Mairiseth Telearat, Cliffwalk]
description: Several maedatha-draped booths flank the faenor-forged railing leading up to the bridge, the oceanside breeze rustling the ivory-traced heartleaf draped across the maedat-shaped fountain at the center of the courtyard.  Entangled curtains of jewel-toned florals partially shade the garden-topped limestone buildings along the pathway, the fragrant canopies highlighted by the naevela-crafted lanterns affixed to the posts.
